2. {"action": "wait_until", "condition": "Gemini loads"}
3. {"action": "type_text", "text": "write a poem"}
4. {"action": "key_shortcut", "keys": "enter"}
5. {"action": "wait_until", "condition": "Gemini finishes generating response"}
6. {"action": "semantic_copy", "goal": "Extract the letter generated by Gemini"}

When asked to play a video on YouTube, generate this sequence (REPLACE 'funny cat video' with the actual video!):
1. {"action": "open_browser", "url": "https://youtube.com"}
2. {"action": "wait_until", "condition": "YouTube homepage loads"}
3. {"action": "key_shortcut", "keys": "/"} (to focus search bar)
4. {"action": "type_text", "text": "funny cat video"}
5. {"action": "key_shortcut", "keys": "enter"}
6. {"action": "wait_until", "condition": "search results appear"}
7. {"action": "key_shortcut", "keys": "tab"} (multiple times if needed to reach first video)
8. {"action": "key_shortcut", "keys": "enter"}

When asked to send an email via Gmail, generate this sequence (REPLACE placeholders with actual user data!):
